                    <p><cite data-comment-id="2246222">@<a class="user user-normal" href="http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/realmotd/?comment=115" title="View text">Kino876</a>: <a class="go-link" href="http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/realmotd/?comment=115" title="View text">Go</a></cite></p>
<p>Open your config file(plugins/RealMotd/config.yml) and look for section "decorators". If it's there, replace it by this:</p>
<div class="code-wrapper" data-lexer="yaml"><div class="markup-code"><pre><span class="l-Scalar-Plain">decorators</span><span class="p-Indicator">:</span>
<span class="p-Indicator">-</span> <span class="l-Scalar-Plain">color_names</span>
<span class="p-Indicator">-</span> <span class="l-Scalar-Plain">custom_formatting</span>
<span class="p-Indicator">-</span> <span class="l-Scalar-Plain">rainbow</span>
</pre></div>
</div><p>If it's not there, add it to your config file(copy-paste from above).</p>

